The application is available for both smartphones and tablets.

It lists 7 wonders of the World in a ListView. On clicking a particular wonder, additional information gets displayed about that wonder.

In the Portrait Mode, the screen shows the list of Wonders. Click a particular activity starts a new Activity which displays the image and descroption of that wonder.

In Landscape mode, the left Pane shows the list of wonders and the right pane shows on top an image of the selected wonder and bottom part shows the  description/details of the wonder. 

The user also has the option to add, edit and delete a wonder from the ListView. All the data is stored in SQLite database.

Functionalities implemented-
1. Fragments and FrameLayout
2. ListView and Dynamic List Adapters
3. Action Bar
4. Android's Database Management- Sqlite
5. Custom Dialogs

How To Use : 

Tap on any wonder name, its image and description will be displayed.

